(52,	'apache重写地址的一点笔记',	'<code>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n\r\n以前用WAMP的时候，直接启用REWRITE MODULE，然后在.htaccess下写入以下内容即可。\r\n<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>\r\nRewriteEngine on\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule . /index.php\r\n</IfModule>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n最近用zend server 7，.htaccess就要改成如下了\r\n<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>\r\nRewriteEngine on\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^/(.*)$ /index.php\r\n</IfModule>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n也可直接创建一个vhost文件，用http.conf包含加载。\r\n如\r\nNameVirtualHost larele.me:80\r\n<VirtualHost *:80>\r\n    DocumentRoot E:/InstalledApp/Zend/Apache2/htdocs/larele\r\n    ServerName larele.me\r\n    RewriteEngine on\r\n    RewriteBase /\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\n    RewriteRule ^/(.*)$ /index.php\r\n</VirtualHost>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n以上经验，还没空去理解为什么这样设置\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</code>',	'<code>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n\r\n以前用WAMP的时候，直接启用REWRITE MODULE，然后在.htaccess下写入以下内容即可。\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine on\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule . /index.php\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n最近用zend server 7，.htaccess就要改成如下了\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine on\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^/(.*)$ /index.php\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n也可直接创建一个vhost文件，用http.conf包含加载。\r\n如\r\nNameVirtualHost larele.me:80\r\n&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\r\n    DocumentRoot E:/InstalledApp/Zend/Apache2/htdocs/larele\r\n    ServerName larele.me\r\n    RewriteEngine on\r\n    RewriteBase /\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\n    RewriteRule ^/(.*)$ /index.php\r\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n以上经验，还没空去理解为什么这样设置\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</code>',	'<code>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n\r\n以前用WAMP的时候，直接启用REWRITE MODULE，然后在.htaccess下写入以下内容即可。\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine on\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule . /index.php\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n最近用zend server 7，.htaccess就要改成如下了\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine on\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^/(.*)$ /index.php\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n也可直接创建一个vhost文件，用http.conf包含加载。\r\n如\r\nNameVirtualHost larele.me:80\r\n&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\r\n    DocumentRoot E:/InstalledApp/Zend/Apache2/htdocs/larele\r\n    ServerName larele.me\r\n    RewriteEngine on\r\n    RewriteBase /\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\n    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\n    RewriteRule ^/(.*)$ /index.php\r\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n以上经验，还没空去理解为什么这样设置\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n</code>',	1442243924,	1442244034,	1,	'',	99,	1),
